title: God Has The Final Say
itunes:title: God Has The Final Say
description:
During times of discouragement, when it seems like you are at the mercy of your circumstances, know that God always has the final say. Whatever you are facing, you can live with confidence knowing that God has you in the palm of His hand. The battle belongs to Him!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
